<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I just read the book. It is full of great stories, however I found some of them kind of soulless, while others are amazing and surprising, with a well<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I just read the book. It is full of great stories, however I found some of them kind of soulless, while others are amazing and surprising, with a well-paced rythm. The best was to be identified in some of the stories, because as a Latin guy I lived in Europe for almost three years: GGM was reading my mind!<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
